members.name: fetchAllHreaModeler
members.description:
Fetches the hrea-modeler for all agents in the DHT

You can subscribe to `knowHreaModeler` to get updated with all the hrea-modeler when this call is done

Warning! Can be very slow

members.name: fetchAgentHreaModeler
members.description: Fetches the hrea-modeler for the given agent

members.name: fetchAgentsHreaModeler
members.description:
Fetches the hrea-modeler for the given agents in the DHT

You can subscribe to knowHreaModeler to get updated with all the hrea-modeler when this call is done

Use this over `fetchAgentHreaModeler` when fetching multiple hrea-modeler, as it will be more performant
